{"tid":658746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光頭人士福音】英大學發現骨質疏鬆藥2日快速增髮","createTime":"2018-05-09T08:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T10:51:55.000Z","uid":13468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e209f52078fca28fa3a7c240456929d96a47d6be","tid":658746,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"【光頭人士福音】英大學發現骨質疏鬆藥2日快速增髮 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國曼徹斯特大學（University of Manchester）研究團隊，發現一種名為WAY-316606的骨質疏鬆藥物，能在短短兩天內促進毛囊生長。研究團隊正希望展開臨床試驗，往後可將這種藥物，加入洗頭水或髮用凝膠等可接觸頭髮毛囊的用品，作局部增髮治療。<br />\n<br />\nWAY-316606最初為治療骨質疏鬆症而開發。曼徹斯特大學首席研究員Nathan Hawkshaw指，這種藥物之前從未被考慮用於治療脫髮。<br />\n<br />\n曼徹斯特大學以40個有禿頭問題男士的毛囊，進行這項研究。Hawkshaw指，實驗結果顯示，WAY-316606能在兩天內，促進毛囊生長，原理是人體內有種天然生成的蛋白質，會阻止毛髮生長，WAY-316606則能抑制這種蛋白質，使毛髮再生。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員對於WAY-316606增髮的成效感樂觀，他們現在希望展開臨床試驗，日後可用來加入洗頭水或髮用凝膠等可接觸頭髮毛囊的用品，為脫髮人士提供局部增髮治療。Hawkshaw又表示，這種WAY-316606的藥物並無副作用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180509/s00005/1525850187582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180509%2Fs00005%2F1525850187582&d=Wasgvqq%2BsjEdEnWNDSVYoE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=0c054bc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180509%2Fs00005%2F1525850187582&h=20a9fbe1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180509/s00005/1525850187582</a>"},{"pid":"3260c38d7e67197e73b985e8b39a4ac4dc16591c","tid":658746,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T08:48:39.000Z","msg":"英國研究..."},{"pid":"8ce5386c445da29aca6a8808cc30e3acd20dcf59","tid":658746,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:51:26.000Z","msg":"藥=毒"},{"pid":"b4eb7c1215ecbc4e53e604eae33b4096ced37d96","tid":658746,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"王子有救喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8707dc3744b89596170f3b0f4041b2ee2aab15fa","tid":658746,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"兩天內促進毛囊生長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但不生髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}